    11 copies of file.setPermissions(QFileDevice::ReadOwner |
    QFileDevice::WriteOwner) scattered across config.cpp,
    sessionmanager.cpp (x2), claudeallowlist.cpp, auditdialog.cpp
    (x4), claudeintegration.cpp (x2), remotecontrol.cpp, and
    auditrulequality.cpp. Two overloads: one for open QFileDevice&
    handles, one for existing path strings. The one 0755 case
    (settingsdialog.cpp hooks script) stays literal by design.
