  * Added: Audit feature-coverage lanes (src/featurecoverage.{cpp,h}).
    Lane 1 (spec↔code drift) extracts backtick-fenced identifier tokens
    from tests/features/*/spec.md and reports ones that no longer
    appear under src/. Lane 2 (CHANGELOG↔feature-test coverage) fuzz-
    matches Added/Fixed bullets against feature-spec titles. Both plug
