    logs drift + cumulative count + worst-case when the event loop
    was blocked. Gated by ANTS_DEBUG=perf.
  * Added: VT throughput benchmark harness — drives four fixed corpora
    through VtParser → TerminalGrid at -O2. Registered under ctest
    label `perf`.
  * Changed: dropdown-flicker suppression extended to QEvent::HoverMove
    / HoverEnter / HoverLeave in MainWindow::eventFilter. Residual
    flicker still visible — pushed to the 0.8.0 roadmap.
  * Fixed: `new-tab` caller-owns-newline contract — newTabForRemote now
    uses sendToPty (raw bytes) instead of writeCommand. Convenience
    "open + run" moved to the new `launch` command.

