ants-terminal (0.7.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * A session's worth of user-facing UI fixes plus a new Debug Mode
    that made them possible. The instrument pinpointed a ~54 Hz
    full-window repaint cascade that had been driving the menubar /
    dropdown / paste-dialog flicker across several releases.
  * Added: Debug Mode (src/debuglog.{h,cpp}). 14 independent
    category toggles (Paint, Events, Input, PTY, VT, Render,
    Plugins, Network, Config, Audit, Claude, Signals, Shell,
    Session) via ANTS_DEBUG env var or Tools → Debug Mode menu.
    Log at ~/.local/share/ants-terminal/debug.log.
  * Added: OSC 133 prompt-on-new-line guard — terminal-side
    equivalent of zsh's PROMPT_SP, works for any shell that emits
    OSC 133 A at prompt start.
  * Fixed: menubar File / Edit / View hover flash. QMenuBar now
    sets autoFillBackground(true) + Qt::WA_StyledBackground, a
    :hover rule mirrors :selected, setNativeMenuBar(false) is
    explicit.
  * Fixed: paste-confirmation dialog rewrote to the async Review-
    Changes pattern (heap QDialog + WA_DeleteOnClose + show()/
    raise()/activateWindow(), no exec(), no QEventLoop).
  * Fixed: Command Palette idle timer churn — QListWidget is now
    lazy-created in show() instead of at MainWindow construction,
    so QAbstractItemView timers don't fire at idle.
  * Fixed: QMainWindow::setAnimated(false) — we have no dock
    widgets; the animator ran continuously at idle.
  * Fixed: Qt UI effect animations disabled globally
    (UI_AnimateMenu, UI_FadeMenu, UI_AnimateCombo, UI_AnimateTooltip,
    UI_FadeTooltip, UI_AnimateToolBox) via
    QApplication::setEffectEnabled.
  * Fixed: titlebar button tooltips removed — a Qt / KWin quirk
    re-fired the QTipLabel show/hide cycle on every frame,
    animating its geometry and cascading through the whole widget
    tree.
  * Changed: TerminalWidget base class QOpenGLWidget → plain
    QWidget. The GL widget composited through the parent's backing
    store and always invalidated the top-level. QPainter path is
    unaffected. GL glyph-atlas renderer dormant in 0.7.4.
