    changes for end users — the binary is bit-identical to 0.6.29 modulo
    the version string.
  * New .claude/settings.json wires a PostToolUse hook on Edit|Write
    that delegates to packaging/hook-on-cmakelists-edit.sh. Runs
    check-version-drift.sh the moment an agent edits CMakeLists.txt
    and surfaces drift via systemMessage — closes the honor-system
    gap that allowed the 0.6.23 packaging slip to ship.
  * New .claude/bump.json recipe consumed by a user-level /bump skill.
    Lists the 6 version-bearing files with templated find/replace,
    plus 4 todos for content the recipe can't synthesise.
  * .gitignore narrowed .claude/ → .claude/* with explicit
    !.claude/settings.json + !.claude/bump.json exceptions so the
    team-shared workflow files commit while developer-local
    settings.local.json and worktrees/ stay ignored.

